original_title: Manhattan: New Chambers Street - Madison Street
text:
At the intersection of New Chambers and Madison Streets. Shown is New Chambers Street, north side, east from Madison Street. Also shown is Madison Street, south side, east from New Chambers, to and including Chestnut Streets. No. 43 New Chambers Street, at the intersection point is a 2-story frame building. The Second and Third Aves., Elevated is seen on New Bowery.

June 6, 1923.

P. L. Sperr.
